name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForCoronaryArteryBypassSurgeryCABG
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Coronary Artery Bypass Surgery (CABG)
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to CABG procedures and is listed as a cardiovascular disease on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes CABG procedures. It includes the initial bypass procedure as well as revisions.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes complications due to CABG.)
